description: Live in the skies of Seattle: Step into this light-filled, top-floor condo & you'll captivated by breathtaking, unobstructed west-facing views of the Puget Sound, Olympic Mountains, & sparkling waterfront—truly the best views in all of Seattle. Inside you'll find soaring ceilings, new flooring & paint, a spacious open-concept layout, & a stylishly updated kitchen w/ quartz counters & SS appliances, PLUS AC! The bedroom offers panoramic views & dual closets W/system. In-unit washer/dryer, solar shades, secure parking w/EV charging potential & storage.  Amenities: 24-hour concierge, pool, hot tub, sauna, gym, view deck, guest suite, Airbnbs Allowed. Steps to Pike Place Market, light rail, Benaroya Hall, Showbox, & top restaurants & more!
